  <Summary>Experience the rabbit action epic that might have been! More than just a precursor to Stan Sakai’s beloved Usagi Yojimbo, his tales of medieval unwits Nilson and Hermy are every bit as funny, exciting, and beautifully illustrated as the saga of the familiar rabbit ronin! Collecting Nilson and Hermy’s complete exploits!

Collects every Nilson story, plus rarely seen extra art!

Newly scanned from Sakai’s original art and colored by Usagi colorist Tom Luth!

Don’t miss Nilson and Hermy in November’s Dark Horse Presents #30!</Summary>
